dcterms:creator: G.-S. Xia
Y. Kim
dcterms:description: DOTA consists of 15 object categories including ‘car’, ‘ship’, and ‘harbor’, with 2,806 aerial images and 188,282 bounding box labels. It is used for oriented object detection in remote sensing.
dcterms:title: DOTA

dcterms:creator: G. Cheng
dcterms:description: DIOR-R surpasses DOTA with its 20 object categories and 192,512 instances captured in 23,463 images. It is also used for oriented object detection in remote sensing.
dcterms:title: DIOR-R
